Package: MLCSUr
Type: Package
Title: Automate Regular Tasks for Users at Midlands and Lancashire Commissioning Support Unit (MLCSU)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Scott","Johnson", email = "scott.johnson2@nhs.net", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Allows the simplification of running routine functions for MLCSU staff.
    Any function that is run regularly by a member of MLCSU staff can be added to the package 
    in order to speed up automation of tasks.
URL: https://github.com/MLCSU/MLCSUr
BugReports: https://github.com/MLCSU/MLCSUr/issues
